    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607423020864111364)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVnk_O3v-3_text","label":"ggVnk_O3v-3_text","default":"<p>And of course, they all work together to combat the aging effects of Progerin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvCGnjY8oY_text","label":"ggvCGnjY8oY_text","default":"<p>But remember, most anti-aging formulas have one big problem...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKVyvCpHsQ_text","label":"ggKVyvCpHsQ_text","default":"<p>They sit on the surface!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggy7rIQ8IZ_text","label":"gggy7rIQ8IZ_text","default":"<p>For instance, collagen creams are super popular and contain beneficial ingredients. But sometimes if you use too much, you're just wasting product because it can't penetrate deeply enough.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWe4MqEErU_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggWe4MqEErU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s15bx1bg.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ945sDpQv_text","label":"ggQ945sDpQv_text","default":"<p>And nobody likes wasting expensive skincare products.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4TdqUVdbO_text","label":"gg4TdqUVdbO_text","default":"<p>This is where our Anti-Progerin Complex is different. Because it's formulated with ingredients with optimal molecular sizes, these ingredients can reach deeper levels of the skin effectively. For that reason, it's my anti-aging complex of choice.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7r5qvWMxe_text","label":"gg7r5qvWMxe_text","default":"<p>And yes, this revolutionary formula is in every jar of <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggw9cD5i4rX_text","label":"ggw9cD5i4rX_text","default":"<p>And when you combine our breakthrough Progeline with Matrixyl 3000, Argireline, and Ceramide – you get what I now consider to be the most powerful, all-in-one anti-aging treatment we've ever created, bar none.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLXl__3CJx_text","label":"ggLXl__3CJx_text","default":"<p>It's a proven, 4-part formula that will address sagging skin, deep wrinkles, and visible aging concerns in their tracks.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6YJNHad45_text","label":"gg6YJNHad45_text","default":"<p>Now, at this time, I should point out that <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> is not necessarily for everyone.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTHYw4XC82_text","label":"ggTHYw4XC82_text","default":"<p>And nobody likes wasting expensive skincare products.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggew1kLS4oE_text","label":"ggew1kLS4oE_text","default":"<p>If you already have what I call \"Perfect Skin Habits\",<br>meaning you:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_0","label":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_0","default":"<p>Never go in the sun</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_1","label":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_1","default":"<p>Always wear sunscreen</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_2","label":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_2","default":"<p>Never make facial expressions</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_3","label":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_3","default":"<p>Eat a perfect diet</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_4","label":"ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_4","default":"<p>And have amazing genetics</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAtnfjME9g_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggAtnfjME9g_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s15bx2bg_2f4e9db2-032c-4fde-b9a8-b874965a52f5.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeDFwdKIEs_text","label":"ggeDFwdKIEs_text","default":"<p>Then you may truly be one of the few women who do not have high Progerin levels... and are already experiencing the benefits of naturally youthful skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggO5ccQiJpN_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggO5ccQiJpN_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s15img1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvY7UmQ_-1_text","label":"ggvY7UmQ_-1_text","default":"<p>However, if you’re like most women who know they have some sun damage, can see visible lines and wrinkles, and don't eat a perfect diet…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggL3SvZSACX_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggL3SvZSACX_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s15img1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1pqLgwEjD_text","label":"gg1pqLgwEjD_text","default":"<p>Then the <strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> was designed just for you.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZYZvkjlD0_text","label":"ggZYZvkjlD0_text","default":"<p>Now, let's talk about how you can get <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> for yourself today.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVtOnNe9Dt_text","label":"ggVtOnNe9Dt_text","default":"<p>You could try to source all these peptides<br>individually, but that would be extremely expensive and time-consuming...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_k2dXBSPj_text","label":"gg_k2dXBSPj_text","default":"<p>So if you'd rather have this incredible formula measured perfectly, and know that every batch was tested for safety, effectiveness, and potency...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj5dUkPDYU_text","label":"ggj5dUkPDYU_text","default":"<p>Then we've created an easy way for you to obtain <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> for yourself.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiPAPSYmtP_text","label":"ggiPAPSYmtP_text","default":"<p>When <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> is available in stores, my distributor tells me it will retail for around $189.00... a great price when you consider how expensive and time-consuming it is to get these potent age-fighting ingredients and peptides.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6WAnzKVzP_text","label":"gg6WAnzKVzP_text","default":"<p>But because you've read this entire report, and I know you're serious about fighting premature aging, I've asked our team to dramatically lower the cost of <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> for a brief period of time.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggC0ekaF1Sg_text","label":"ggC0ekaF1Sg_text","default":"<p>So if you order today through this page, you can get MiamiMD's <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> for just <strong>$129.00.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzlwR45GSn_text","label":"ggzlwR45GSn_text","default":"<p><strong>That's an instant savings of $60.00!</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpBxiHMJwQ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggpBxiHMJwQ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/My_fine_lines_are_barely_visible_and_my_skin_looks_firmer_and_more_lifted._My_face_finally_looks_youthful_again_the_confidence_is_real._Elena_58_Verified_Vitro_Customer_1_copy-Photoro.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggC4lZ-ixS1_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggC4lZ-ixS1_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/savebg.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQFdnGDHyw_text","label":"ggQFdnGDHyw_text","default":"<p><strong>Save</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:29px;\"><strong>$60</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYVkKshpTU_text","label":"ggYVkKshpTU_text","default":"<p>So if you order today through this page, you can get Vitro's <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> for just <strong>$129.00.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd6HPVOQMR_text","label":"ggd6HPVOQMR_text","default":"<p><strong>That's an instant savings of $60.00!</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTRnJXbZLU_text","label":"ggTRnJXbZLU_text","default":"SPECIAL REPORT-ONLY OFFER UP TO 30% OFF"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJKKfuLCpl_text","labe